  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Using a Ranged Weapon, you can spend <strong>2 AP</strong> and <strong>1 SP</strong> to launch a volley of projectiles.</p>\n<p>Choose a point within your Weapon&rsquo;s range. Make a single <strong>Attack Check </strong>and compare it against the <strong>PD </strong>of all creatures of your choice within 1 Space of the chosen point.</p>\n<p><strong>Attack Hit:</strong> You deal 2 Piercing damage to each creature.</p>\n<p><strong>Extra Damage &amp; Effects: </strong>If you attempt to add additional damage or effects to your <strong>Attack Check </strong>(such as Class Features or Attack Maneuvers) you must select one target of your choice. The additional damage and effects only apply to them.</p>\n<p>The Attack Check still benefits from Heavy Hits and beyond against each individual target</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Technique Enhancements</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Impairing Volley:</strong>&nbsp;<strong>(1 SP)&nbsp;</strong>Force each creature within the area to make a <strong>Physical Save</strong>. <br><strong>Failure:</strong> They are <strong>Impaired </strong>(DisADV on Physical Checks) until the end of your next turn.</li>\n<li><strong>Blanket of Arrows:</strong>&nbsp;<strong>(1 SP) </strong>Increase the area to 3 Spaces from the chosen point.</li>\n<li><strong>Line of Arrows:</strong>&nbsp;<strong>(1 SP) </strong>Target any creature occupying a space in a line from you to the chosen point, within your weapon&rsquo;s range.</li>\n</ul>",
